"use strict";(globalThis.webpackChunkkodi_website=globalThis.webpackChunkkodi_website||[]).push([[130],{7735(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"/2026/03/01/simplify-blog-kodi-studios","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2026/03/01/simplify-blog-kodi-studios","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/kodistudios.github.io/tree/main/blog/2026-03-01-simplify-blog-kodi-studios.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-03-01-simplify-blog-kodi-studios.md","title":"Simplify Blog Workflow for Kodi Studios Website","description":"Kodi Studios is an old website, it has gone through multiple iterations. Some","date":"2026-03-01T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"authors":"nikoari"},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Switch Images to Cloudinary","permalink":"/blog/2026/02/22/switch-to-cloudinary"}},"content":"Kodi Studios is an old website, it has gone through multiple iterations. Some\\nwere more successful than others. Started off with WordPress, then moved to more\\nmodern and sustainable solutions like Docusaurus. It really takes an effort to\\nget website to good condition. However, if approached one step at a time, this\\nbig effort can be fully achieved.\\n\\nOne lesson is to not get overwhelmed. Tech stack changes every other year, but\\nas long as you keep and control your content, you have the power to migrate,\\ntransform it.\\n\\nDon\'t be afraid to start new website, even in 2026 with social media all around.\\nSocial media basically controls what it shows and what it doesn\'t. Your own\\nwebsite is your own presence on internet.\\n\\n## Accomplishments\\n\\n### Kodi Studios Website https://kodistudios.com\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Blog \\\\\\n  Migrated to new blogging pattern that removes noise and allows creator to\\n  concentrate on blog content and message. \\\\\\n  One of core improvements is enabling markdown formatting, which improves\\n  readability not only for rendered blog pages, but also for original source\\n  markdown files. Super Excited for this improvement. \\\\\\n  Blogging can become a pleasant zen activity, rather than a battle with\\n  formatting utilities.\\n- \u26f5 Linters \\\\\\n  Added Linters and other Best Practices into Kodi Studios website. It should\\n  make it easier to maintain, update.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Next Effort\\n\\n### Personal Site https://aristov.net\\n\\n- \ud83c\udf88 Align DNS Settings\\\\\\n  Need to switch https://aristov.net to point to https://nikolaiaristov.com \\\\\\n  This will allow full merge.\\\\\\n  Also, need to consider:\\\\\\n  https://aristov.eu\\n\\n### Kodi Studios Website https://kodistudios.com\\n\\n- \ud83d\udc1d Incorporate Best Practices 2026 \\\\\\n  There are still few improvements that still can be done to really make Kodi\\n  Studios shine. They also include some cleanup and will make it even easier to\\n  futher make Kodi Studios awesome!"},{"id":"/2026/02/22/switch-to-cloudinary","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2026/02/22/switch-to-cloudinary","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/kodistudios.github.io/tree/main/blog/2026-02-22-switch-to-cloudinary.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-02-22-switch-to-cloudinary.md","title":"Switch Images to Cloudinary","description":"Finally found replacement of OneDrive with Cloudinary.","date":"2026-02-22T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"authors":"nikoari"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Simplify Blog Workflow for Kodi Studios Website","permalink":"/blog/2026/03/01/simplify-blog-kodi-studios"},"nextItem":{"title":"Upload New Images","permalink":"/blog/2026/02/16/upload-new-images-decisions"}},"content":"Finally found replacement of OneDrive with Cloudinary.\\n\\n## Accomplishments\\n\\n### Images Research\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Cloudinary\\\\\\n  Created end-to-end Image solution for WebSites using Cloudinary. So far, I\'m\\n  impressed with Cloudinary speed and ease of configuration. Hopefully, it will\\n  be a nice solution for WebSite Images and other assets.\\\\\\n  New Cloudinary asset manager scripts are available at:\\\\\\n  https://github.com/KodiStudios/cloudinary-embed\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n### Personal Site https://nikolaiaristov.com\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:\\\\\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com\\n\\n- \ud83d\udcd6 Improved Getting Started Documentation\\\\\\n  Includes Development.md and ReadMe.md\\n\\n- \ud83c\udf09 Switched from PnP to Node Modules\\\\\\n  This will help with future project maintenance Yarn V4 Node Modules makes it\\n  easier for IDE Editors and other utilities to manage the project\\n\\n- \ud83c\udf07 Switched End Line setting\\\\\\n  Minor, but important so that repo can work well on all platforms, including\\n  Windows and macOS\\n\\n## Next Effort\\n\\n### Personal Site https://aristov.net\\n\\n- \ud83c\udf88 Align DNS Settings\\\\\\n  Need to switch https://aristov.net to point to https://nikolaiaristov.com\\n\\n  This will allow full merge.\\\\\\n  Also, need to consider:\\\\\\n  https://aristov.eu"},{"id":"/2026/02/16/upload-new-images-decisions","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2026/02/16/upload-new-images-decisions","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/kodistudios.github.io/tree/main/blog/2026-02-16-upload-new-images-decisions.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-02-16-upload-new-images-decisions.md","title":"Upload New Images","description":"It turns out that OneDrive is rather slow to display images through shared URLs.","date":"2026-02-16T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"authors":"nikoari"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Switch Images to Cloudinary","permalink":"/blog/2026/02/22/switch-to-cloudinary"},"nextItem":{"title":"Update OneDrive Embed Project","permalink":"/blog/2026/02/07/update-onedrive-embed"}},"content":"It turns out that OneDrive is rather slow to display images through shared URLs.\\nThus, I ventured onto journey to find alternatives to OneDrive.\\n\\n## Accomplishments\\n\\n### Images Research\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Cloudify\\\\\\n  After real world testing of OneDrive as image provider through URLs, it turned\\n  out that OneDrive is extremely slow. Like it takes about 5 seconds to load a\\n  single image. Started to explore other providers. One promising solution is\\n  Cloudify. However, during my research, I ran out of VsCode Copilot Credits \ud83d\ude05\\n  Which just shows how important AI utilities have become nowadays.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Next Effort\\n\\n### Personal Site https://aristov.net\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:\\\\\\n  https://aristov.net"},{"id":"/2026/02/07/update-onedrive-embed","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2026/02/07/update-onedrive-embed","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/kodistudios.github.io/tree/main/blog/2026-02-07-update-onedrive-embed.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-02-07-update-onedrive-embed.md","title":"Update OneDrive Embed Project","description":"Of course a nice website needs to have great content, not only text but","date":"2026-02-07T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"authors":"nikoari"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Upload New Images","permalink":"/blog/2026/02/16/upload-new-images-decisions"},"nextItem":{"title":"New Nikolai Aristov Website","permalink":"/blog/2026/01/31/new-personal-website"}},"content":"Of course a nice website needs to have great content, not only text but\\npictures. For personal website https://nikolaiaristov.com there needs to be a\\nway to store pictures for it.\\n\\nOne of answers is OneDrive Embed Script. It allows users to store pictures on\\nOneDrive and then reference them from their website.\\n\\n## Accomplishments\\n\\n### OneDrive Embed Script\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Updated OneDrive Embed Project\\\\\\n  Tons of goodness, updated yarn, linting, TypeScript, testing\\\\\\n  Updated to use latest and greatest patterns\\\\\\n  Added OneDrive Api Integration test\\\\\\n  This allows to easily verify OneDrive Embed Script\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Next Effort\\n\\n### Personal Site https://nikolaiaristov.com\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:\\\\\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com\\n\\n### Picturethrill App\\n\\n- \ud83d\udc23 New Picturethrill App Version\\\\\\n  Release to Kodi Studios Website\\n\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates\\\\\\n  Update Picturethrill App to 2026"},{"id":"/2026/01/31/new-personal-website","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2026/01/31/new-personal-website","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/kodistudios.github.io/tree/main/blog/2026-01-31-new-personal-website.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-01-31-new-personal-website.md","title":"New Nikolai Aristov Website","description":"Lots of great progress around Kodi Studios. Recently, created new lifestyle","date":"2026-01-31T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"authors":"nikoari"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Update OneDrive Embed Project","permalink":"/blog/2026/02/07/update-onedrive-embed"},"nextItem":{"title":"Enter New Year 2026","permalink":"/blog/2026/01/24/enter-new-year-2026"}},"content":"Lots of great progress around Kodi Studios. Recently, created new lifestyle\\npersonal website:\\\\\\nhttps://nikolaiaristov.com\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Accomplishments\\n\\n### Metro Evolved Website\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Updated Docusaurus Instructions\\\\\\n  As part of creation of new website https://nikolaiaristov.com, also updated\\n  instructions on Docusaurus:\\\\\\n  https://metroevolved.com/docs/category/create-site\\n\\n  Now it\'s easier more than ever to create low-cost websites\\n\\n### Tonivo App\\n\\nhttps://kodistudios.com/docs/tonivo\\n\\n- \ud83d\udc23 Enabled Tonivo App on Lower Windows Versions\\\\\\n  Originally, Tonivo App was able to run only on most recent Windows. However,\\n  it would be nice to support to more Windows versions, including some older\\n  ones. This really increases users who can download and use Tonivo App. Now,\\n  all of the following versions are supported:\\n  - Windows 11\\n  - Windows 10\\n  - Windows 8\\n  - Windows 7\\n\\n## Next Effort\\n\\n### Picturethrill App\\n\\n- \ud83d\udc23 New Picturethrill App Version\\\\\\n  Release to Kodi Studios Website\\n\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates\\\\\\n  Update Picturethrill App to 2026\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Add Personal Picture onto lifestyle site:\\\\\\n  https://nikolaiaristov.com"},{"id":"/2026/01/24/enter-new-year-2026","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/2026/01/24/enter-new-year-2026","editUrl":"https://github.com/KodiStudios/kodistudios.github.io/tree/main/blog/2026-01-24-enter-new-year-2026.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-01-24-enter-new-year-2026.md","title":"Enter New Year 2026","description":"Welcome to a fresh new year at Kodi Studios. As we step into 2026 with the full","date":"2026-01-24T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[],"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Nikolai Aristov","title":"Digital Creator","url":"https://github.com/NikoAri","imageURL":"https://github.com/NikoAri.png","key":"nikoari","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"authors":"nikoari"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"New Nikolai Aristov Website","permalink":"/blog/2026/01/31/new-personal-website"}},"content":"Welcome to a fresh new year at Kodi Studios. As we step into 2026 with the full\\nmomentum of AI, we are excited to roll out updates across both\\nhttps://kodistudios.com and https://metroevolved.com. The latest version of the\\nTonivo App is now live, delivering even more value and delight for our users.\\nWe\'re looking forward to a year of amazing websites and inspiring apps. Here\'s\\nto making 2026 a memorable year along with our users and community.\\n\\n## Accomplishments\\n\\n### Kodi Studios Website\\n\\n- \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Fixes\\\\\\n  Fixed Edit Links\\\\\\n  Fixed DNS\\\\\\n  Fixe Yaml Publish Pipeline\\n\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates\\\\\\n  Updated Kodi Studios Website to latest packages, including Docusaurus V3,\\n  TypeScript, Node.js, Yarn V4 etc.\\n\\n### Metro Evolved Website\\n\\n- \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f New Logo\\\\\\n  Created New Logo for MetroEvolved website\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n- \u26f5 New Content Entries\\\\\\n  Added Entries for DNS and Apple Magic Mouse on Windows\\n\\n- \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Fixes\\\\\\n  Fixed Website Layout\\n\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates\\\\\\n  Updated Kodi Studios Website to latest packages, including Docusaurus V3,\\n  TypeScript, Node.js, Yarn V4 etc.\\n\\n### Tonivo App\\n\\n- \ud83d\udc23 New Tonivo App Version\\\\\\n  Released new version of Tonivo Windows App and added download link to Kodi\\n  Studios website:\\\\\\n  [https://kodistudios.com/docs/tonivo](https://kodistudios.com/docs/tonivo)\\n\\n- \ud83c\udf88 Single Exe\\\\\\n  Created option for Single Exe in Tonivo App\\\\\\n  Download it at:\\\\\\n  [Tonivo.Desktop.exe](https://github.com/KodiStudios/tonivo-release/releases/download/26.1.21/Tonivo.Desktop.exe)\\n\\n## Next Effort\\n\\n### Picturethrill App\\n\\n- \ud83d\udc23 New Picturethrill App Version\\\\\\n  Release to Kodi Studios Website\\n\\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Updates\\\\\\n  Update Picturethrill App to 2026"}]}}')}}]);